#: ../../../getting_started/using_js.md:3
msgid ""
"[vtk.js](https://kitware.github.io/vtk-js/docs/) is an implementation of VTK "
"in JavaScript that consists of an ES6 class library which can be integrated "
"into any web application. See [here](https://kitware.github.io/vtk-js/docs/"
"#What-is-the-difference-with-VTK-C)  to learn more about the differences "
"between VTK C++ and vtk.js."
